1.0.name: wordpress/outbound-click-tracker
1.0.description: The Outbound Click Tracker Plugin uses JavaScript to detect and record clicks on an off-site links. JavaScript security model limits which links it can track. It will not track links that advertisers or affiliates have placed in an iframe tag. It will not track Google Adsense clicks. It will not track JavaScript redirects from an onClick event. Top links in the last 5 days are displayed on the settings page as well as details for each Click. As an option the plugin can make outbound links open in a new window.
